{"tid":1428157,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議民間記者會參考狗隻記者會示威用火機菜刀為攻擊性武器","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T09:34:35.000Z","uid":4322,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e87f7a0177c9c72e2fbc4a353f85bc85885f4b79","tid":1428157,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:59:47.000Z","msg":"示範用火機燒紙<br />\n示範用菜刀劈肉<br />\n要求差佬拘捕所有買火機菜刀呢兩樣攻擊性武器既人<br />\n並查封所有出售攻擊性武器的軍火庫！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時天旱禁酒，釀者有刑。吏於人家索得釀具，論者欲令與作酒者同罰。雍與先主游觀，見一男女行道，謂先主曰：「彼人欲行淫，何以不縛？」先主曰：「卿何以知之？」雍對曰：「彼有其具，與欲釀者同。」先主大笑，而原欲釀者。<br />\n<br />\n《三國志．蜀書．簡雍傳》<br />\n<br />\n火鳳燎原：<br />\n將荒謬推到極點的簡雍。<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n有一次蜀漢遇上大旱，於是下令禁酒，後來發展到連釀酒都有罪，官兵更從民家搜得釀酒器具，朝中有人主張要他們與釀酒的人同罰。簡雍明白再這樣下去民眾一定會有所不滿，於是趁有機會隨劉備一同外出時，在車上看見一對男女走過，簡雍就對劉備說：「他們就要做淫亂之事了，怎麼不將他們抓起來？」劉備問道：「你怎麼知道？」簡雍就回答：「他們都有可以淫亂的器具，和那些有釀酒器具的人一樣。」劉備聽罷大笑，就不再追究家藏釀酒器具的民家了。<br />\n<br />\n簡雍用一句簡單可笑的話，將荒謬推到極點，就化解了蜀漢的一場執政危機，可惜現在沒有這種智者在官場上，更沒有如劉備般明白事理以及有氣度的主公。藉著一千七百多年的事情可以告訴大家一件事，人類根本沒有進步過，更沒有吸取歷史的教訓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/586182821420713/posts/2421483617890615?s=829095206&amp;substory_index=0&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F586182821420713%2Fposts%2F2421483617890615%3Fs%3D829095206%26substory_index%3D0%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ0%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=52ef0308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/586182821420713/posts/2421483617890615?s=829095206&amp;substory_index=0&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港警察 可笑至極！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ac4202cc87a829d4a8850359c044362b9d6dd670","tid":1428157,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:00:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e13c3553dd3e61e66bd12ef4aca7254b7825a055","tid":1428157,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e4e8fa5314da93a8fc29d77819561725d8fe8131","tid":1428157,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9133fa22694c8b6dabd7a81de0634edbb162e21","tid":1428157,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"唔洗啦 電筒都燒得著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e97d94062a83a70c71cda3cff0cdc929c47818","tid":1428157,"uid":151110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:06:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9226ad669deaab5b45e47d9e9a6e7a06533f2860","tid":1428157,"uid":151554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"人類冇進步過"},{"pid":"19615003a07320bef4fe67c1f21697276300ce6e","tid":1428157,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c68dab51bbfca10b0255bb4e60dd4e2c412c4eb3","tid":1428157,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"2aaee0351fe9d8f74224ecda2fa257426c9f3d38","tid":1428157,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"直接用鉛筆拮穿張紙就得啦"}]}